Source string: And then everything went black.
Translation: And then everything went black.

Source string: I believe you've been abducted, probably by Coach Oleander.
Translation: I believe you've been abducted, probably by Coach Oleander.

Source string: He's trying to take over the world.
Translation: He's trying to take over the world.

Source string: Oh, Morry.
Translation: Oh, Morry.

Source string: Well, if you find my body, give it a little shake, will you?
Translation: Well, if you find my body, give it a little shake, will you?

Source string: In the mean time, you can shake it in here as much as you want!
Translation: In the mean time, you can shake it in here as much as you want!

Source string: Yow!
Translation: Yow!

Source string: Ugh!
Translation: Ugh!

Source string: Oof!
Translation: Уф!

Source string: Press {WhiteButton} to Levitate.
Translation: Press {WhiteButton} to Levitate.

Source string: Press {AButton} to Bubble Bounce.
Translation: Press {AButton} to Bubble Bounce.

Source string: Press {AButton} while airborne to Double Bubble Bounce over the gap.
Translation: Press {AButton} while airborne to Double Bubble Bounce over the gap.

Source string: Bubble Bounce then press the {LeftFlipper} while airborne to float over the gap.
Translation: Bubble Bounce then press the {LeftFlipper} while airborne to float over the gap.

Source string: Bubble Bounce then press {LeftFlipper} while airborne to float over the gap.
Translation: Bubble Bounce then press {LeftFlipper} while airborne to float over the gap.

Source string: Press {LeftFlipper} while airborne to float.
Translation: Press {LeftFlipper} while airborne to float.

Source string: Float in an updraft for extra lift.
Translation: Float in an updraft for extra lift.

Source string: Respawn kickout activated! If you miss a jump, return here!
Translation: Respawn kickout activated! If you miss a jump, return here!

Translation: Best Time:

Translation: Your Time:

Translation: Levitation Learner's Permit

Translation: Press {BlackButton} to Levitate.

Source string: Press {RightFlipper} to Levitate.
Translation: Press {RightFlipper} to Levitate.

Source string: Reset race
Translation: Reset race

Source string: Use your Thought Bubble to map your LEVITATION power to a button on the controller.
Translation: Use your Thought Bubble to map your LEVITATION power to a button on the controller.

Source string: Haha! Yay! Raz learned Telekinesis! Right on!
Translation: Haha! Yay! Raz learned Telekinesis! Right on!

Source string: That's nice, darling, but why don't you help us instead?
Translation: That's nice, darling, but why don't you help us instead?

Source string: GO
Translation: GO

Source string: LOSE
Translation: LOSE

Source string: READY
Translation: READY

Source string: SET
Translation: SET

Source string: WIN
Translation: WIN

Source string: Right on, Raz! You learned firestarting! Good for you!
Translation: Right on, Raz! You learned firestarting! Good for you!

Source string: Wow, you're really good at Telekinesis, Raz! That's awesome!
Translation: Wow, you're really good at Telekinesis, Raz! That's awesome!

Source string: Hee hee hee! Yay! Firestarting practice! Woo!
Translation: Hee hee hee! Yay! Firestarting practice! Woo!

Source string: What's this all about, eh?
Translation: What's this all about, eh?

Source string: Careful, eh? My hair goes up in flames and we're all goners.
Translation: Careful, eh? My hair goes up in flames and we're all goners.

Source string: Okay, I really don't like being up this high.
Translation: Okay, I really don't like being up this high.

Source string: Oh man. I hope I don't get much hotter. That would be uncomfortable.
Translation: Oh man. I hope I don't get much hotter. That would be uncomfortable.

Source string: Put me down partner or I'll show you what a good shot I am!
Translation: Put me down partner or I'll show you what a good shot I am!

Source string: Move along, little doggy. Nothin' to burn here.
Translation: Move along, little doggy. Nothin' to burn here.

Source string: Hey! Grow up, Razputin!
Translation: Hey! Grow up, Razputin!

Source string: If you don't stop trying to burn me right now I am going to SCREAM!
Translation: If you don't stop trying to burn me right now I am going to SCREAM!

Source string: Finally! I'm being TAKEN! They've finally come for me! Hey! It's just you. PUT ME DOWN!
Translation: Finally! I'm being TAKEN! They've finally come for me! Hey! It's just you. PUT ME DOWN!

Source string: Hm. Atmospheric changes in effect. Adjusting helmet thermostat.
Translation: Hm. Atmospheric changes in effect. Adjusting helmet thermostat.

Source string: Are you sure you want to reset the race?
Translation: Are you sure you want to reset the race?
